# Best Practices

* Use `inherit systemd`
* Always define `SYSTEMD_SERVICE:${PN}`
* Enable only required services
* Use `Restart=always` for critical daemons
* Add dependency rules (`After=`)
* Test service startup after boot
* Use `journalctl` for debugging
* Keep service files simple and maintainable

